lScope> </bibl> </cit>) was prob. read by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristarch.</author> </bibl> in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0434.tlg001:348\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Cratin.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">348</biblScope></bibl>, and shd. perh. be read in Ar.l.c.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐδεὶς πόκον εἰς γναφεῖον φέρει</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Arcesil.</author> </bibl> </cit> ap. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.624</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}